deleteAllPowerPreroutes(25.10)                  deleteAllPowerPreroutes(25.10)

Name
       deleteAllPowerPreroutes  -  Removes all power preroutes from the floor-
       plan

Syntax
       deleteAllPowerPreroutes

       [-help]

       Removes all power preroutes from the floorplan. Use this command  after
       importing the design.

Parameters
       None

       -help  Outputs  a brief description of the deleteAllPowerPreroutes com-
              mand.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man deleteAllPowerPreroutes

Related Information
              * Floorplanning the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

